{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Compassion:"},{"time":3000,"text":"what does it look like?"},{"time":7000,"text":"Come with me to 915 South Bloodworth Street"},{"time":12000,"text":"in Raleigh, North Carolina, where I grew up."},{"time":16000,"text":"If you come in you will see us: evening time,"},{"time":19000,"text":"at table -- set for ten but not always all seats filled --"},{"time":26000,"text":"at the point when dinner is ready to be served."},{"time":30000,"text":"Since mom had eight kids,"},{"time":32000,"text":"sometimes she said she couldn't tell who was who and where they were."},{"time":37000,"text":"Before we could eat, she would ask,"},{"time":40000,"text":"\"Are all the children in?\""},{"time":43000,"text":"And if someone happened to be missing,"},{"time":46000,"text":"we would have to, we say, \"Fix a plate\" for that person, put it in the oven,"},{"time":53000,"text":"then we could say grace, and we could eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"Also, while we were at the table,"},{"time":60000,"text":"there was a ritual in our family:"},{"time":63000,"text":"when something significant had happened for any one of us --"},{"time":67000,"text":"whether mom had just been elected as the president of the PTA,"},{"time":72000,"text":"or whether dad had gotten an assignment at the college of our denomination,"},{"time":78000,"text":"or whether someone had won the jabberwocky contest for talent --"},{"time":84000,"text":"the ritual at the family was, once the announcement is made,"},{"time":88000,"text":"we must take five, ten minutes to do what we call \"make over\" that person --"},{"time":94000,"text":"that is, to make a fuss over the one who had been honored in some way."},{"time":100000,"text":"For when one is honored, all are honored."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"Also, we had to make a report on our extended \"visited\" members,"},{"time":112000,"text":"that is, extended members of the family,"},{"time":116000,"text":"sick and elderly, shut in."},{"time":118000,"text":"My task was, at least once a week, to visit Mother Lassiter"},{"time":123000,"text":"who lived on East Street,"},{"time":125000,"text":"Mother Williamson who lived on Bledsoe Avenue,"},{"time":128000,"text":"and Mother Lathers who lived on Oberlin Road."},{"time":131000,"text":"Why? Because they were old and infirm,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and we needed to go by to see if they needed anything."},{"time":139000,"text":"For mom said, \"To be family, is to care and share and to look out for one another."},{"time":146000,"text":"They are our family.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"And, of course, sometimes there was a bonus for going."},{"time":151000,"text":"They would offer sweets or money."},{"time":154000,"text":"Mom says, \"If they ask you what it costs to either go shopping for them,"},{"time":158000,"text":"you must always say, 'Nothing.'"},{"time":160000,"text":"And if they insist, say, 'Whatever you mind to give me.'\""},{"time":165000,"text":"This was the nature of being at that table."},{"time":168000,"text":"In fact, she indicated that if we would do that,"},{"time":173000,"text":"not only would we have the joy of receiving the gratitude"},{"time":178000,"text":"from the members of the extended family,"},{"time":180000,"text":"but she said, \"Even God will smile, and when God smiles,"},{"time":187000,"text":"there is peace, and justice, and joy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"So, at the table at 915, I learned something about compassion."},{"time":197000,"text":"Of course, it was a minister's family,"},{"time":200000,"text":"so we had to add God into it."},{"time":203000,"text":"And so, I came to think that mama eternal, mama eternal,"},{"time":210000,"text":"is always wondering: Are all the children in?"},{"time":215000,"text":"And if we had been faithful in caring and sharing,"},{"time":220000,"text":"we had the sense that justice and peace would have a chance in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"Now, it was not always wonderful at that table."},{"time":227000,"text":"Let me explain a point at which we did not rise to the occasion."},{"time":232000,"text":"It was Christmas, and at our family, oh, what a morning."},{"time":237000,"text":"Christmas morning, where we open up our gifts,"},{"time":240000,"text":"where we have special prayers, and where we get to the old upright piano"},{"time":244000,"text":"and we would sing carols. It was a very intimate moment."},{"time":247000,"text":"In fact, you could come down to the tree to get your gifts and get ready to sing,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and then get ready for breakfast without even taking a bath or getting dressed,"},{"time":258000,"text":"except that daddy messed it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"There was a member of his staff who did not have any place"},{"time":265000,"text":"on that particular Christmas to celebrate."},{"time":269000,"text":"And daddy brought Elder Revels to the Christmas family celebration."},{"time":276000,"text":"We thought he must be out of his mind."},{"time":278000,"text":"This is our time. This is intimate time."},{"time":281000,"text":"This is when we can just be who we are,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and now we have this stuffy brother"},{"time":286000,"text":"with his shirt and tie on, while we are still in our PJs."},{"time":290000,"text":"Why would daddy bring Elder Revels?"},{"time":296000,"text":"Any other time, but not to the Christmas celebration."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"And mom overheard us and said,"},{"time":302000,"text":"\"Well, you know what? If you really understand the nature of this celebration,"},{"time":308000,"text":"it is that this is a time where you extend the circle of love."},{"time":314000,"text":"That's what the celebration is all about."},{"time":317000,"text":"It's time to make space, to share the enjoyment of life in a beloved community.\""},{"time":326000,"text":"So, we sucked up."},{"time":328000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"But growing up at 915, compassion was not a word to be debated;"},{"time":337000,"text":"it was a sensibility to how we are together."},{"time":343000,"text":"We are sisters and brothers united together."},{"time":347000,"text":"And, like Chief Seattle said, \"We did not spin the web of life."},{"time":353000,"text":"We're all strands in it."},{"time":355000,"text":"And whatever we do to the web, we do to ourselves.\""},{"time":359000,"text":"Now that's compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"So, let me tell you, I kind of look at the world this way."},{"time":364000,"text":"I see pictures, and something says, \"Now, that's compassion.\""},{"time":369000,"text":"A harvested field of grain, with some grain in the corners,"},{"time":378000,"text":"reminding me of the Hebrew tradition"},{"time":381000,"text":"that you may indeed harvest,"},{"time":383000,"text":"but you must always leave some on the edges,"},{"time":387000,"text":"just in case there's someone who has not"},{"time":390000,"text":"had the share necessary for good nurture."},{"time":395000,"text":"Talk about a picture of compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"I see -- always, it stirs my heart --"},{"time":402000,"text":"a picture of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr."},{"time":406000,"text":"walking arm in arm with Andy Young and Rabbi Heschel"},{"time":411000,"text":"and maybe Thich Nhat Hanh and some of the other saints assembled,"},{"time":416000,"text":"walking across the bridge and going into Selma."},{"time":420000,"text":"Just a photograph."},{"time":422000,"text":"Arm in arm for struggle."},{"time":425000,"text":"Suffering together in a common hope that we can be brothers and sisters"},{"time":432000,"text":"without the accidents of our birth or our ethnicity"},{"time":437000,"text":"robbing us of a sense of unity of being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441000,"text":"So, there's another picture. Here, this one. I really do like this picture."},{"time":446000,"text":"When Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. was assassinated,"},{"time":450000,"text":"that day, everybody in my community was upset."},{"time":457000,"text":"You heard about riots all across the land."},{"time":462000,"text":"Bobby Kennedy was scheduled to bring an inner city message in Indianapolis."},{"time":471000,"text":"This is the picture. They said,"},{"time":474000,"text":"\"It's going to be too volatile for you to go.\""},{"time":477000,"text":"He insisted, \"I must go.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"So, sitting on a flatbed truck,"},{"time":484000,"text":"the elders of the community are there,"},{"time":486000,"text":"and Bobby stands up and says to the people,"},{"time":490000,"text":"\"I have bad news for you."},{"time":492000,"text":"Some of you may not have heard that Dr. King has been assassinated."},{"time":496000,"text":"I know that you are angry,"},{"time":499000,"text":"and I know that you would almost wish to have the opportunity"},{"time":502000,"text":"to enter now into activities of revenge. But,\""},{"time":505000,"text":"he said, \"what I really want you to know is that I know how you feel."},{"time":512000,"text":"Because I had someone dear to me snatched away."},{"time":518000,"text":"I know how you feel.\""},{"time":521000,"text":"And he said, \"I hope that you will have the strength to do what I did."},{"time":527000,"text":"I allowed my anger, my bitterness, my grief to simmer a while,"},{"time":533000,"text":"and then I made up my mind that I was going to make a different world,"},{"time":538000,"text":"and we can do that together.\""},{"time":540000,"text":"That's a picture. Compassion? I think I see it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544000,"text":"I saw it when the Dalai Lama came to the Riverside Church while I was a pastor,"},{"time":551000,"text":"and he invited representatives of faith traditions from all around the world."},{"time":558000,"text":"He asked them to give a message,"},{"time":561000,"text":"and they each read in their own language a central affirmation,"},{"time":568000,"text":"and that was some version of the golden rule:"},{"time":573000,"text":"\"As you would that others would do unto you,"},{"time":577000,"text":"do also unto them.\""},{"time":582000,"text":"Twelve in their ecclesiastical or cultural or tribal attire"},{"time":588000,"text":"affirming one message."},{"time":591000,"text":"We are so connected that we must treat each other"},{"time":595000,"text":"as if an action toward you is an action toward myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"One more picture while I'm stinking and thinking about the Riverside Church:"},{"time":606000,"text":"9/11. Last night at Chagrin Fall,"},{"time":612000,"text":"a newspaperman and a television guy said,"},{"time":616000,"text":"\"That evening, when a service was held at the Riverside Church,"},{"time":622000,"text":"we carried it on our station in this city."},{"time":626000,"text":"It was,\" he said, \"one of the most powerful moments of life together."},{"time":634000,"text":"We were all suffering."},{"time":636000,"text":"But you invited representatives of all of the traditions to come,"},{"time":642000,"text":"and you invited them."},{"time":644000,"text":"'Find out what it is in your tradition"},{"time":648000,"text":"that tells us what to do when we have been humiliated,"},{"time":652000,"text":"when we have been despised and rejected.'"},{"time":656000,"text":"And they all spoke out of their own traditions,"},{"time":659000,"text":"a word about the healing power of solidarity, one with the other.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":666000,"text":"I developed a sense of compassion sort of as second nature,"},{"time":673000,"text":"but I became a preacher."},{"time":675000,"text":"Now, as a preacher, I got a job. I got to preach the stuff,"},{"time":679000,"text":"but I got to do it too."},{"time":681000,"text":"Or, as Father Divine in Harlem used to say to folks,"},{"time":685000,"text":"\"Some people preach the Gospel."},{"time":688000,"text":"I have to tangibilitate the Gospel.\""},{"time":690000,"text":"So, the real issue is: How do you tangibilitate compassion?"},{"time":696000,"text":"How do you make it real?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699000,"text":"My faith has constantly lifted up the ideal,"},{"time":703000,"text":"and challenged me when I fell beneath it."},{"time":707000,"text":"In my tradition, there is a gift that we have made to other traditions --"},{"time":713000,"text":"to everybody around the world who knows the story of the \"Good Samaritan.\""},{"time":721000,"text":"Many people think of it primarily in terms of charity,"},{"time":728000,"text":"random acts of kindness."},{"time":731000,"text":"But for those who really study that text a little more thoroughly,"},{"time":737000,"text":"you will discover that a question has been raised"},{"time":740000,"text":"that leads to this parable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742000,"text":"The question was: \"What is the greatest commandment?\""},{"time":746000,"text":"And, according to Jesus, the word comes forth,"},{"time":749000,"text":"\"You must love yourself,"},{"time":751000,"text":"you must love the Lord your God with all your heart, mind and soul,"},{"time":755000,"text":"and your neighbor as yourself.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":759000,"text":"And then the person asked, \"Well, what do you mean, 'neighbor?'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"And he answered it by telling the story of the man who fell among thieves,"},{"time":771000,"text":"and how religious authorities went the other way,"},{"time":777000,"text":"and how their supporters in the congregation went the other way;"},{"time":781000,"text":"but an unsuspecting, despised person came along,"},{"time":786000,"text":"saw the man in need,"},{"time":789000,"text":"provided oil and wine for his wounds,"},{"time":793000,"text":"put him on his own transportation,"},{"time":798000,"text":"and took him to the inn"},{"time":801000,"text":"and asked the innkeeper, \"Take care of him.\""},{"time":805000,"text":"And he said, \"Here, this is the initial investment,"},{"time":812000,"text":"but if needs continue, make sure that you provide them."},{"time":818000,"text":"And whatever else is needed, I will provide it and pay for it when I return.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"This always seemed to me to be a deepening"},{"time":828000,"text":"of the sense of what it means to be a Good Samaritan."},{"time":832000,"text":"A Good Samaritan is not simply one whose heart is touched"},{"time":835000,"text":"in an immediate act of care and charity,"},{"time":839000,"text":"but one who provides a system of sustained care -- I like that,"},{"time":843000,"text":"'a system of sustained care ' -- in the inn, take care."},{"time":847000,"text":"I think maybe it's one time when the Bible talks about a healthcare system"},{"time":852000,"text":"and a commitment to do whatever is necessary --"},{"time":856000,"text":"that all God's children would have their needs cared for,"},{"time":859000,"text":"so that we could answer when mommy eternal asks, \"In regards to health,"},{"time":865000,"text":"are all the children in?\" And we could say yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":868000,"text":"Oh, what a joy it has been to be a person seeking to tangibilitate compassion."},{"time":877000,"text":"I recall that my work as a pastor"},{"time":880000,"text":"has always involved caring for their spiritual needs;"},{"time":885000,"text":"being concerned for housing, for healthcare,"},{"time":889000,"text":"for the prisoners, for the infirm, for children --"},{"time":893000,"text":"even the foster care children for whom no one can even keep a record"},{"time":899000,"text":"where they started off, where they are going."},{"time":901000,"text":"To be a pastor is to care for these individual needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":906000,"text":"But now, to be a Good Samaritan -- and I always say,"},{"time":910000,"text":"and to be a good American -- for me,"},{"time":913000,"text":"is not simply to congratulate myself for the individual acts of care."},{"time":918000,"text":"Compassion takes on a corporate dynamic."},{"time":923000,"text":"I believe that whatever we did around that table at Bloodworth Street"},{"time":930000,"text":"must be done around tables and rituals of faith"},{"time":935000,"text":"until we become that family, that family together"},{"time":941000,"text":"that understands the nature of our unity."},{"time":944000,"text":"We are one people together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":948000,"text":"So, let me explain to you what I mean when I think about compassion,"},{"time":954000,"text":"and why I think it is so important that right at this point in history."},{"time":960000,"text":"We would decide to establish this charter of compassion."},{"time":965000,"text":"The reason it's important is because this is a very special time in history."},{"time":975000,"text":"It is the time that, biblically, we would speak of as"},{"time":979000,"text":"the day, or the year, of God's favor."},{"time":983000,"text":"This is a season of grace."},{"time":985000,"text":"Unusual things are beginning to happen."},{"time":989000,"text":"Please pardon me, as a black man, for celebrating"},{"time":991000,"text":"that the election of Obama was an unusual sign"},{"time":996000,"text":"of the fact that it is a year of favor."},{"time":1000000,"text":"And yet, there is so much more that needs to be done."},{"time":1007000,"text":"We need to bring health and food and education"},{"time":1012000,"text":"and respect for all God's citizens, all God's children,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"remembering mama eternal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1021000,"text":"Now, let me close my comments by telling you"},{"time":1025000,"text":"that whenever I feel something very deeply,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"it usually takes the form of verse."},{"time":1033000,"text":"And so I want to close with a little song."},{"time":1037000,"text":"I close with this song -- it's a children's song --"},{"time":1041000,"text":"because we are all children at the table of mama eternal."},{"time":1047000,"text":"And if mama eternal has taught us correctly,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"this song will make sense, not only to those of us who are a part of this gathering,"},{"time":1057000,"text":"but to all who sign the charter for compassion."},{"time":1060000,"text":"And this is why we do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062000,"text":"The song says, ♫ \"I made heaven so happy today, ♫"},{"time":1066000,"text":"♫ Receiving God's love and giving it away ♫"},{"time":1070000,"text":"♫ When I looked up, heaven smiled at me ♫"},{"time":1074000,"text":"♫ Now, I'm so happy. Can't you see? ♫"},{"time":1077000,"text":"♫ I'm happy. Look at me. I'm happy. Can't you see? ♫"},{"time":1082000,"text":"♫ Sharing makes me happy, makes heaven happy too ♫"},{"time":1086000,"text":"♫ I'm happy. Look at me. I'm happy. Can't you see? ♫"},{"time":1090000,"text":"♫ Let me share my happy loving smile with you. ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1094000,"text":"That's compassion. (Applause)"}]}]}